com.vmware.nsx_policy.model

Class IPSecVpnSessionStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.model.IPSecVpnSessionStatistics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StaticStructure, Structure, Serializable

    public final class IPSecVpnSessionStatistics
extends Object
implements Serializable, StaticStructure
    IPSec VPN session statistics represents statistics on an NSX-T type of enforcement point. It gives aggregated statistics of all policies for all the tunnels.
